Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.03,0:21:08.48,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fad(400,400)}You held out a small hand
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.61,0:21:10.37,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fad(400,400)}Smiling wide to you
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.44,0:21:14.37,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fad(400,400)}It was so natural
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.95,0:21:19.54,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fad(400,400)}It may have no meaning
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.77,0:21:25.31,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fad(400,400)}But it is something I cannot do
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.64,0:21:31.38,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fad(400,400)}You touched my hand without thinking
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.38,0:21:35.17,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fad(400,400)}That it was nice for me
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.10,0:21:43.49,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fad(400,400)}All the times we believed
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.61,0:21:51.74,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fad(400,400)}That the words in our hands we will draw
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.87,0:21:59.94,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fad(400,400)}Maybe it wasn't 'cause\N you're holding my hand now
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.13,0:22:11.06,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fad(400,400)}Every moment, everywhere
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.20,0:22:16.43,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fad(400,400)}I can feel, I can feel
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.76,0:22:21.61,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fad(400,400)}When I'm holding you from bad
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.67,0:22:28.98,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fad(400,400)}You will learn
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.03,0:21:08.48,ED-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fad(400,400)}你伸出的稚嫩雙手
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.61,0:21:10.37,ED-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fad(400,400)}一如那燦爛的微笑
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.44,0:21:14.37,ED-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fad(400,400)}那樣自然
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.95,0:21:19.54,ED-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fad(400,400)}也許沒有過多的意義
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.77,0:21:25.31,ED-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fad(400,400)}卻讓我可望而不可即
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.64,0:21:31.38,ED-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fad(400,400)}你輕觸我的掌心 不帶一絲猶疑
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.38,0:21:35.17,ED-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fad(400,400)}撫慰著我的心靈
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.10,0:21:43.49,ED-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fad(400,400)}我們始終堅信
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.61,0:21:51.74,ED-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fad(400,400)}手心的誓言 是未來的藍圖
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.87,0:21:59.94,ED-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fad(400,400)}但此刻 我只想擁有你的溫熱
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.13,0:22:11.06,ED-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fad(400,400)}無論何時 無論何地
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.20,0:22:16.43,ED-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fad(400,400)}我都可以感知到你
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.76,0:22:21.61,ED-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fad(400,400)}當我從逆境中將你扶起
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.67,0:22:28.98,ED-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fad(400,400)}你將懂得我的心意
